        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Today, we successfully ported Casbin to Node.js, which is named as:
<a href="https://github.com/casbin/node-casbin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">node-Casbin</a>.</p><p><strong>node-Casbin</strong> shares the similar usage and API
